definitions.definition: Something which is believed to possess, contain, or cause spiritual or magical powers; an amulet or a talisman .
A figure representing the spirit of a deity, human, or animal; an idol or voodoo doll .
Sexual attraction to or arousal at something abnormally sexual or nonsexual , such as an object or a nonsexual part of the body.
examples: I know a guy who has a foot fetish .

definitions.definition: An irrational or abnormal preoccupation or fixation on some object or activity; an obsession .

main_definition: Something which is believed to possess, contain, or cause spiritual or magical powers; an amulet or a talisman . [from the early 17th c.]
secondary_definitions: ( animism , dated ) A figure representing the spirit of a deity, human, or animal; an idol or voodoo doll .
( countable , uncountable ) Sexual attraction to or arousal at something abnormally sexual or nonsexual , such as an object or a nonsexual part of the body. [from the early 19th c.]
An irrational or abnormal preoccupation or fixation on some object or activity; an obsession . [from the 19th c.]
